"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-fourth-turning-is-here-and-end-times-3439006b?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">&#39;The Fourth Turning&#39; and &#39;End Times&#39; Review: Big Wheel</a> </h3><div class="media-object scope-
